{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"05c6844222","title":"中国革命的伟大世界意义","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d1976acbdc","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"05c6844222"}],"tags":[{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4679fc3f20","type":"paragraph","text":"在文化革命中立新功","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"035415aed7","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"badde2d404","type":"paragraph","text":"老干部过去有功劳，但是不能靠吃老本，要很好地在无产阶级文化大革命运动中炼改造自己，要立新功，立新劳。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"154a88ff04","type":"paragraph","text":"（转引自六月一日《人民日报》）关于夏收的指示","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"96bf32bfe6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月三日）","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"b4477357b3","type":"paragraph","text":"积极行动超来夏收夏种，目前正进人两夏大忙季节，南方已开始收割。今年全国复收作物生长很好。今年的夏收，各级领导同志应特别重视，立即投人夏收夏种。各地要组织学生、机关干部、工人、解放军，以劳力、音力、技术力量，大力支持人民公融，做到颗粒归仓，严防阶级敌人破坏。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"2787759a4b","type":"paragraph","text":"关于中央各部运动的指示","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"81a815d024","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"85e84cd4d8","type":"paragraph","text":"“全国的形势比我们预料的要慢，中央各部要慢。”开始说三、四月出眉目，前几天主席说“比预料的晚了一个季度，不是三、四、五月了，而是六、七月了。与其估计快一点，不如估计慢一点，与其估计很容易，不如估计困难一点。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"a2addcead0","type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命的伟大世界意义","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"812f3b15ea","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）中国革命的胜利，主要不是搞地下斗争，而是武装斗争。就是全世界都黑了，只要中国是光明的，那世界就有希望，没什么问题。","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"94166730bc","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命，首先要把北京、上海、天津这几个地方搞好。上海就是工人这个队伍比较好，所以上海的局势中央也比较放心。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"},{"id":"9ee2b45d9a","type":"paragraph","text":"（六月八日张春桥同志传达）314","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222"}],"page":{"id":"4c534841a6","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"05c6844222","start":327,"end":327}}}},"__N_SSG":true}